    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1927-01-04T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1927-01-04T17:00:00-05:00" n="716"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d716">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">711.672/532b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the High
                        Commissioner in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bristol</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-01-04T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 4, 1927—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1. Treaty will be taken up in secret executive session of Senate today.<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d716fn1">The general treaty between the United States and
                        Turkey was signed at Lausanne, Aug. 6, 1923 (<ref
                            target="frus1923v02#pg_1153">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1923, vol. <hi
                                rend="smallcaps">ii</hi>, p. 1153</ref>). For previous
                        correspondence concerning the ratification of the treaty, see <ref
                            target="frus1926v02#pg_974">
                            <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, 1926, vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">ii</hi>,
                            pp. 974</ref> ff.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
